- Add integration tests using testcontainers (PostgreSQL + Redis in Docker)
- Add E2E tests with Playwright (containerized)
- Configure Trivy security scanning in CI pipeline
- Implement container security (non-root users, read-only filesystems)
- Add automated DB migration job to deployment pipeline
