### Phase 3: Production Deployment Automation - **3-4 days**
- Set up automated deployment via GitHub Actions (`deploy.yml`)
- Configure blue/green or rolling deployment strategy
- Add smoke tests post-deployment
- Write runbooks for Docker operations
- Document rollback procedures (Docker image tags)
- Set up automated DB backups (pg_dump in cron container)

### Total for Production-Ready AUT Deployment: **12-16 days (~2-3 weeks)**

